s="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 hover:text-black dark:hover:text-white transition-colors" href="/service/missing-persons">Missing Persons</a><a class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 hover:text-black dark:hover:text-white transition-colors" href="/service/background-checks">Background Checks</a><a class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 hover:text-black dark:hover:text-white transition-colors" href="/service/skip-tracing">Skip Tracing</a><a class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 hover:text-black dark:hover:text-white transition-colors" href="/service/digital-forensics">Digital Forensics</a></div></div><div><h4 class="font-black text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4 border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 pb-2">Newsroom</h4><div class="flex flex-col gap-2.5"><a class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 hover:text-black dark:hover:text-white transition-colors" href="/service">PI &amp; Investigative Services</a><a class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 hover:text-black dark:hover:text-white transition-colors" href="/about">About Objective Wire</a><a class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 hover:text-black dark:hover:text-white transition-colors" href="/authors">Our Authors</a><a class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 hover:text-black dark:hover:text-white transition-colors" href="/editorial-standards">Editorial Standards</a><a class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 hover:text-black dark:hover:text-white transition-colors" href="/corrections">Corrections</a><a class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 hover:text-black dark:hover:text-white transition-colors" href="/get-help/contact">Contact Us</a><a class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 hover:text-black dark:hover:text-white transition-colors" href="/site-index">Site Index</a></div></div><div><h4 class="font-black text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4 border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 pb-2">Newsletter</h4><section class="relative w-full overflow-hidden rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-900 via-gray-800 to-black px-6 py-10 shadow-xl border border-gray-700"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute -top-16 -right-16 w-64 h-64 rounded-full bg-purple-600/20 blur-3xl"></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute -bottom-12 -left-12 w-48 h-48 rounded-full bg-pink-600/15 blur-2xl"></div><div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col items-center text-center gap-4 max-w-xl mx-auto"><h3 class="text-2xl font-extrabold text-white leading-tight">Stay ahead of every story</h3><p class="text-gray-400 text-sm max-w-sm">Breaking news, deep-dives, and editor picks, delivered straight to your inbox. No spam, ever.</p><form class="flex w-full max-w-md gap-2 mt-2"><input type="email" required="" placeholder="your@email.com" class="flex-1 rounded-xl border border-gray-600 bg-gray-800/80 px-4 py-3 text-white placeholder-gray-500 text-sm focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-purple-500 focus:border-transparent disabled:opacity-50 transition" value=""/><button type="submit" class="shrink-0 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-600 to-pink-600 px-5 py-3 text-sm font-bold text-white shadow hover:from-purple-500 hover:to-pink-500 active:scale-95 disabled:opacity-60 transition-all">Subscribe</button></form><p class="text-gray-600 text-xs mt-1">Free · Unsubscribe anytime · No ads</p></div></section></div></div></div><div class="border-t border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800"><div class="container max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-8"><div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8"><div><p class="text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-400 mb-2">Our Mission</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">Objective Wire is a 501(c)(3) nonprofit investigative agency incorporated in Wyoming and operating throughout Texas. Private investigative services, field work, and public-interest reporting, documented and verified.</p></div><div><p class="text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-400 mb-2">Editorial Independence</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">Editorial decisions are made independently of advertising and sponsorship. Sponsored content is clearly labeled. Errors are corrected publicly and transparently.<!-- --> <a class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 underline" href="/editorial-standards">Read our editorial standards.</a></p></div><div><p class="text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-400 mb-2">Contact</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">Newsroom tips, corrections, press inquiries, and case submissions:<!-- --> <a class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 underline" href="/get-help/contact">contact form</a>. Copyright complaints:<!-- --> <a class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 underline" href="/copyright">copyright policy</a>.</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mt-2">2921 E 17th St Building 3, APT 3205, Austin, TX 78702<br/><a href="tel:+15754950323" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 underline">(575) 495-0323</a></p></div></div></div></div><div class="border-t border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800 bg-white dark:bg-black"><div class="container max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-5 flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-3"><div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-xs text-gray-400"><span class="font-bold text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">Objective Wire</span><span class="text-gray-300 dark:text-gray-700">|</span><span>501(c)(3) Wyoming Nonprofit · Investigative Services Throughout Texas</span><span class="text-gray-300 dark:text-gray-700 hidden sm:inline">|</span><span class="hidden sm:inline">Austin, Texas</span></div><div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-4 text-xs text-gray-400"><span>© 2026 Objective Wire. All rights reserved.</span><a class="hover:text-black dar